---
---

<section class="relative" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-bg-dark) 0%, #1a1510 100%);">
  <div
    class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px"
    style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--color-atomic-orange), transparent);"
  ></div>

  <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto text-center py-20 px-6 fade-in">
    <div class="text-5xl mb-6" style="filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(232,101,26,0.5));">
      ☢
    </div>
    <h2
      class="font-heading text-5xl font-bold uppercase tracking-[4px] mb-4"
      style="color: var(--color-text-primary);"
    >
      加入核子前沿
    </h2>
    <p class="text-sm leading-[1.8] mb-10" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
      人类文明的未来，掌握在那些敢于直面原子之火的人手中。<br />
      如果您拥有超越时代的远见与勇气，ATOMIC-7研究所期待您的加入。
    </p>
    <button
      class="clip-btn font-heading text-sm font-semibold tracking-[3px] uppercase px-8 py-3.5 text-white transition-all duration-150 cursor-pointer"
      style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-atomic-orange) 0%, var(--color-atomic-orange-dim) 100%); border: 2px solid var(--color-atomic-orange); box-shadow: 0 4px 0 var(--color-atomic-orange-dim), 0 6px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.3);"
      onmouseover="this.style.transform='translateY(-2px)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 6px 0 var(--color-atomic-orange-dim), 0 8px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.3), 0 0 20px rgba(232,101,26,0.3)'"
      onmouseout="this.style.transform=''; this.style.boxShadow='0 4px 0 var(--color-atomic-orange-dim), 0 6px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.3)'"
    >
      提交准入申请
    </button>
  </div>
</section>
